1. Create a workflow dictionary on startup -
    sructure : {
        workflow_name1: {...},
        workflow_name2: {...}
    }
2. Create a single workflow 
    structure: {
        workflow_name: {
            steps: {
                actor_1: {...}
            },
            start: actor_1
        }
    }
3. Actor: 
    structure: {
        actor_1: {
            resolver:fn,
            type: emitter/publisher
        }
    }